originalText.text: I have been looking for a dentist for a year and finally found a really great one! I get nervous getting dental work done but Dr. Nawlo is very gentle! He takes his time to explains everything clearly. The assistants there were also very nice, attentive both when I called & during my visits! Thank you for your great service!

originalText.text: I am terrified of the dentist and I had several cavities and my mom told me to go to DR. Nawlo, it took me a year plus lots of pain to finally decided to go. Let me tell you I wish I would’ve gone before, He is the best ever very gentle and more important he validates your feelings and make sure you feel comfortable and explains everything he is doing I had zero pain and my anxiety went from 100 to zero I would go back to him in a blink of an eye. If you are afraid of the dentist don’t look any further this is your Doctor. Thank you so much for helping me Dr. Nawlo you won a patient for life!!

originalText.text: Dr. Nawlo is a great dentist, I am VERY scared of the dentist and he treated me with kindness and compassion. He was very gentle during my examination and cleaning I had 3 cavities which sucks but Dr Nawlo was so gentle I didn't feel a thing. Dr. Nawlo is the only dentist I will ever go to. My appointment was in the morning and the receptionist did not look happy to be there, I asked her a question and she shrugged her shoulders and said I don't know and went back to playing games on her phone.  I won't deduct a star because of the receptionist because of the 5 star experience with Dr. Nawlo

originalText.text: I had not been to the dentist for 5 years, but really my previous experience was not the best, definitely this Doctor is very good and attentive, he carefully checked my teeth and in the same consultation he repaired three pieces of my teeth, which left me very happy since one of them had broken recently and it was like new, the place was very clean, its receptionist very attentive and polite and there was no waiting and very important they speak Spanish. 5 stars.
